original_title: UFC Fight Night 76: Holohan vs. Smolka
overview: UFC Fight Night 76: Holohan vs. Smolka was a mixed martial arts event held on October 24, 2015, at 3Arena in Dublin, Ireland. A flyweight bout between Paddy Holohan and Louis Smolka was promoted to serve as the event's new headliner.
title: UFC Fight Night 76: Holohan vs. Smolka
